description:
Sydney's parents are from the Middle East, but he was born in the United States.

I love his eyes and his dark hair!

He's 19 and just graduated from high school where he was on the football and wrestling team.

He says he's mostly straight, but has thought about being with another guy. However, it hasn't happened yet.

"I was watching a little bit of bi-porn," he said. "I think I could do that."

He has no interest in being with any guys that he knows, though.

"It would probably have to be pretty random," he said...
title: Sydney
